{"tid":2264464,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再叫佢哋做泛民","createTime":"2020-10-30T15:56:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T20:21:05.000Z","uid":373438,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c36f6af82c4294ba1bda409aabdfab1b821c33eb","tid":2264464,"uid":373438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:56:56.000Z","msg":"泛民，原本就係解廣泛嘅民主派。從定義上連梁天琦陳浩天都可以包攬喺嗰個範圍入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為咗令到形容佢哋嘅名稱更加準確，應該叫佢哋做傳統民主派、甚至係民主建制派(事實上佢哋相信體制內改革<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)佢哋真係堂堂正正喺建制內嘅改革主義者<br />\n<br />\n即使我對佢哋有不滿，呢個post主要唔係想污名化佢哋，只係希望我哋用字上真係能夠保持清晰，因為我哋要諗清楚佢哋叫咩名先可以真正了解佢哋嘅本質。<br />\n<br />\n我個人唔討厭佢哋，反而覺得佢哋好可悲。我退一萬步當佢哋真係為香港好，咁佢哋就真係私底下賴人鞋底，再喺公眾前面鬧多佢哋幾句就博人哋會肯讓步，佢哋表面上做足門面功夫做到個反對派嘅樣，到最後又做唔到反對派應該做嘅嘢。佢哋根本睇死香港最後冇未來，先至做樣安慰下香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f552468f948f17a98e34c2b10db23b62d1f0bc","tid":2264464,"uid":373438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:57:48.000Z","msg":"樓主P牌、五毛、分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19aadf537f2a38bfd925925f164274e200efe725","tid":2264464,"uid":373438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"75f552468f948f17a98e34c2b10db23b62d1f0bc","tid":2264464,"uid":373438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:57:48.000Z","msg":"樓主P牌、五毛、分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:58:38.000Z","msg":"[詳細定義]何謂分化撚？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2237882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2237882</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"51df0c82aaa08878b158a925dc5dad2953d35167","tid":2264464,"uid":282494,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:02:03.000Z","msg":"體制內改革無問題<br />\n都係有咩做咩盡可能做<br />\n問題係佢地偽黃"},{"pid":"15a28cf77719e052c316a463bbf39464112dbb6c","tid":2264464,"uid":163174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T20:02:05.000Z","msg":"岩 <br />\n所謂屌泛民/撐泛民都根本就係政治白痴，連咩叫泛民都未知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n泛民= 所有撐民主反建制既派別"},{"pid":"f2f6f84f90396ff206c865abc82bd0db96312c9d","tid":2264464,"uid":65770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T20:21:05.000Z","msg":"我叫開忠誠反對派"}]}